            <title>[HBASE-4771] Script to List HRegion Availability</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-4771</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;One critical feature necessary to completely automate production pushes is the ability to recognize when HBase has successfully made all regions available for reads/writes (step prior to HBCK).  Created script to display region availability status and stall until all onlined regions are actually available.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
